{"tid":810332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵】周一售票  七旬翁今早6時排隊  望偕妻搭首班車一日遊","createTime":"2018-09-08T01:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T04:08:42.000Z","uid":136994,"like":63,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b8bbe1400b190e962a5c20cce5eb4bca358077a6","tid":810332,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180908/s00001/1536367364652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180908%2Fs00001%2F1536367364652&d=NcR7R2YgvSmy%2FZlfdaZChTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d20405d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180908%2Fs00001%2F1536367364652&h=73b0c3de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180908/s00001/1536367364652</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180908/s00001/224cc80dace228368a4e54be4610009b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180908%2Fs00001%2F224cc80dace228368a4e54be4610009b.jpg&h=b850d6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段將於本月23日通車，港鐵昨日宣布下周一（10日開始）預售車票，有市民今日一早已經到現場排隊輪候。<br />\n<br />\n70多歲的退休人士梁先生家住北區，他今早6時多已經到柯士甸站排隊，會通宵留守兩日。梁先生說，希望買通車日首班車的車票，雖然不清楚首班車開往什麼地方，但仍計劃與太太搭首班車一日遊。<br />\n<br />\n梁先生說，過去也有到內地旅行，主要乘搭巴士或飛機，從未搭過高鐵。他說，高鐵香港段開通後，在香港搭高鐵出行會較方便，亦有計劃乘搭長途班次，例如香港到北京的列車，雖然車程長，但他說自己已退休，時間較多，不擔心車程長。<br />\n<br />\n根據港鐵昨天的宣布，西九總站的售票機及櫃枱會由下周一(10日)早上8時開始售票（需要先在港鐵柯士甸站D2出口排隊輪候），而電話及網站則會由中午12時開始售票。車票開售首日只預售10日內車票，每人限購8張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">廢老以為高鐵好似啲動物節美食節咁第一個入場可以1蚊買高鐵飛吖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瞓你個街啦<br />\n仲有2晩吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f1c00d23b6763c861319a20dbcf9a39192f4efa1","tid":810332,"uid":29675,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:43:35.000Z","msg":"住北區山長水遠走去西九搭膠鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢老D思想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b85e4feb7298f758df4367e1170b878bea8c59","tid":810332,"uid":19012,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:45:09.000Z","msg":"70多歲的退休人士梁先生家住北區<br />\n<br />\n住北區重要搭膠鐵<br />\n<br />\n真係浪費地球資源"},{"pid":"9d774784cb839cc7de226735ba6b47b96de9e855","tid":810332,"uid":31305,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1c00d23b6763c861319a20dbcf9a39192f4efa1","tid":810332,"uid":29675,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:43:35.000Z","msg":"住北區山長水遠走去西九搭膠鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢老D思想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:46:33.000Z","msg":"仆街廢老兩蚊搭車又唔洗做野<br />\n零成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891d615e320ce735e90ee0e6bb0920897d1cfc28","tid":810332,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:46:45.000Z","msg":"住東涌果班廢老 幾年後又會入屯門搭去赤臘角架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7d8a074aa7f7d3911f44c66988c2874bae165c","tid":810332,"uid":191815,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:47:14.000Z","msg":"家住北區 南下坐高鐵 上去一日遊頂多咪去深圳北 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6b7c686e8340edcc053c3612f192f99f471e6a","tid":810332,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:47:37.000Z","msg":"如果係真